window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the twenty-sixth century, humanity is at war with the Xenophobes, and the planet Loki is the next battleground. </p> <p>Dev Cameron joined the military to fly a starship but is rated unsuitable and grudgingly accepts an assignment with the ground forces, piloting a massive walking tank (a warstrider). But Cameron may yet get a chance at glory when he makes a discovery about the alien foes that could change the course of the war.</p>"; 
